$lang['Hexadecimal is a way of representing binary data in human-readable form. It was developed in the 19th century to allow computers to store large amounts of information.'] = 'I-Hexadecimal yindlela yokumela idatha yokubini kwimo efundeka ngumntu. Yaphuhliswa ngenkulungwane ye-19 ukuvumela iikhompyutha ukugcina isixa esikhulu solwazi.';
$lang['You can use hexadecimal to convert between decimal and binary values. For example, converting 10011011001010 into hexadecimal would result in 0x4F. This means that the value 4F represents the binary number 100110110010110.'] = 'Ungasebenzisa i-hexadecimal ukuguqula phakathi kwedesimali kunye namaxabiso okubini. Umzekelo, ukuguqula i-10011011001010 ibe yi-hexadecimal kuya kubangela i-0x4F. Oku kuthetha ukuba ixabiso 4F limele inombolo yokubini 100110110010110.';
$lang['In mathematics and computer science, hexadecimal (also base 16, or hex) is a positional numeral system with a radix, or base, of 16. It uses sixteen distinct symbols, most often the symbols 0–9 to represent values zero to nine, and A, B, C, D, E, F (or alternatively a–f) to represent values ten to fifteen. For example, the hexadecimal number 2AF3 is equal, in decimal, to (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) , or 10,995.'] = 'Kwimathematika kunye nesayensi yekhompyutha, i-hexadecimal (kwakhona i-base 16, okanye i-hex) yinkqubo yamanani e-positional ene-radix, okanye isiseko, se-16. Isebenzisa iimpawu ezilishumi elinesithandathu ezihlukeneyo, ngokuphindaphindiweyo iisimboli 0-9 ukumela ixabiso le-zero ukuya kwi-9. kunye no-A, B, C, D, E, F (okanye ngenye indlela a–f) ukumela amaxabiso eshumi ukuya kwishumi elinesihlanu. Umzekelo, inani le-hexadecimal 2AF3 lilingana, ngokwedesimali, ukuya (2 × 163) + (10 × 162) + (15 × 161) + (3 × 160) okanye 10,995.';
$lang['Each hexadecimal digit represents four binary digits (bits) (also called a "nibble"), and the primary use of hexadecimal notation is as a human-friendly representation of binary coded values in computing and digital electronics. For example, byte values can range from 0 to 255 (decimal) but may be more conveniently represented as two hexadecimal digits in the range 00 through FF. Hexadecimal is also commonly used to represent computer memory addresses.'] = 'Idijithi nganye ene-hexadecimal imele amadijithi okubini amane (amasuntswana) (ekwabizwa ngokuba &quot;yi-nibble&quot;), kwaye usetyenziso oluphambili lwe-hexadecimal notation luphawu olunobuhlobo lomntu lwamaxabiso okubini anekhowudi kwikhompyutha nakwi-elektroniki yedijithali. Umzekelo, amaxabiso e-byte anokususela ku-0 ukuya ku-255 (idesimali) kodwa angamelwa ngokufanelekileyo njengamasuntswana amabini anehexadecimal kuluhlu lwe-00 ukuya kwi-FF. I-Hexadecimal ikwaqhele ukusetyenziswa ukubonisa iidilesi zememori yekhompyuter.';
$lang['Hex is an abbreviation of Hexadecimal, which is based on a base -16 structure and is used for simplifying how instructions to computers are represented. This 16 symbols number system was developed as a means of inhibiting an 8-bit binary number, so data can be encoded into computers effortlessly. It can be imprinted and typed using two different hex digits with each hex digit demonstrating a nibble or perhaps a 4-bits format.'] = 'I-Hex sisishunqulelo se-Hexadecimal, esekelwe kwisiseko -16 isakhiwo kwaye sisetyenziselwa ukwenza lula indlela imiyalelo kwiikhompyutha ezimele ngayo. Le nkqubo yeesimboli ezili-16 yaphuhliswa njengendlela yokuthintela i-8-bit binary number, ngoko ke idatha inokufakwa ngekhowudi kwiikhomputha ngaphandle komzamo. Inokuprintwa kwaye ichwethezwe kusetyenziswa idijithi ezimbini ezahlukeneyo zeheksi kunye nedijithi nganye ye-hex ebonisa i-nibble okanye mhlawumbi ifomathi ye-4-bits.';
$lang['This number system uses 16 symbols that are represented in a range from 0-9 or A-F. The 0–9 represent numbers up to nine whereas A-F is represented by the numeric 10–15. As compared to the other three types of number systems, the hexadecimal numeral system is considered to be the most effective one.'] = 'Le nkqubo yamanani isebenzisa iisimboli ezili-16 ezimelwe kuluhlu olusuka ku-0-9 okanye AF. U-0–9 umele amanani ukuya kutsho kwisithoba ngoxa i-AF imelwe ngamanani u-10–15. Xa kuthelekiswa nezinye iintlobo ezintathu zeesistim zamanani, inkqubo yamanani e-hexadecimal ithathwa njengeyona isebenzayo.';
$lang['Your hexadecimal code is invalid'] = 'Ikhowudi yakho ye-hexadecimal ayisebenzi';
